routingMIB.name: routingMIB
routingMIB.contactinfo: Shubhra Garg Postal: 330 Codman Hill Road, Boxboro MA, 01719. Tel: +1 978 264 1904 Fax: +1 978 264 1929 E-mail: shubhra@coriolisnet.com
routingMIB.description: The MIB module for coriolis proprietary routing variables

routeAdvPrefixTable.name: routeAdvPrefixTable
routeAdvPrefixTable.description: The routing prefix table. For NEs(including the GNE) whose subnet number is included in this table, the subnet route gets added to the routing tables and propagated by routing protocols rather than the host route

routeAdvPrefixEntry.name: routeAdvPrefixEntry
routeAdvPrefixEntry.description: Entry containing information about subnet numbers and the corresponding masks

routeAdvSummAddr.name: routeAdvSummAddr
routeAdvSummAddr.description: The subnet number, used as an index in the table

routeAdvSummMask.name: routeAdvSummMask
routeAdvSummMask.description: The subnet mask, used as an index in the table

routeAdvSummRowStatus.name: routeAdvSummRowStatus
routeAdvSummRowStatus.description: The row status is used to add entries to the prefix table or delete those entries

routeAdvSummRipAdminCost.name: routeAdvSummRipAdminCost
routeAdvSummRipAdminCost.description: This parameter is the RIP metric that is used when the entry is added to the RIP routing table

routeAdvSummOspfAdminCost.name: routeAdvSummOspfAdminCost
routeAdvSummOspfAdminCost.description: This parameter is the OSPF metric that is used when the entry is added to the RIP routing table

routeAdvSummNumSuppressedRoutes.name: routeAdvSummNumSuppressedRoutes
routeAdvSummNumSuppressedRoutes.description: This is the number of host routes that have been suppressed by this prefix route if this prefix route has been added to the RIP routing table.
